    <section class="page-section template-section">
        <div class="section-content-container">
            <h2 class="section-title">
                Project<br />
                Templates
            </h2>
            <div class="section-desc">Coding templates based on .Net MAUI / Blazor that enables high quality speedy cross-platform development for web, android and iOS and also has pixel-perfect, ready to use UIs.</div>
            <div class="template-card">
                <div class="template-content-continaer">
                    <div class="template-name">TodoTemplate</div>
                    <div class="template-desc">
                        TodoTemplate is based on ASP.NET core, identity, web api and ef core for the server side + blazor at client side.<br />
                        It allows you building Android, iOS, Windows, Web applications from single code base.
                    </div>
                    <a class="template-link" href="/todo-template/overview">Read more about TodoTemplate <span class="template-link-arrow"></span></a>
                </div>
                <div class="template-img"></div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

